{"tid":1612974,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母 又多隻眼","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:57:41.000Z","uid":218238,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dff2ae20a1b00460b89e5807e1a90ae5af21ecc6","tid":1612974,"uid":218238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"印尼女記者右眼將永久失明<br />\n<br />\n本地印尼語傳媒SUARA女記者Veby Mega Indah日前在灣仔站行人天橋採訪遊行時，疑被數米外的警員擎槍射中右眼眼眉，眼球沒有破裂。Indah的代表律師韋智達今晚（2日）表示，醫生經診治後告知，Indah的右眼將永久失明，其瞳孔因外力衝擊破裂，永久損傷程度有待Indah進行手術後才能評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191002/s00001/1570016000256/代表律師-醫生稱印尼女記者右眼將永久失明\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191002%2Fs00001%2F1570016000256%2F%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%A5%B3%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8F%B3%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%87%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%A4%B1%E6%98%8E&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=dbfd0841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191002%2Fs00001%2F1570016000256%2F%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%A5%B3%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8F%B3%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%87%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%A4%B1%E6%98%8E&h=d32de476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191002/s00001/1570016000256/代表律師-醫生稱印尼女記者右眼將永久失明</a>"},{"pid":"22b339590b442227ea86ef47ee205bd5354ef652","tid":1612974,"uid":218238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母還眼"},{"pid":"e7f884fe0caa2f192f5ab9c1fb7f6d0500effcd1","tid":1612974,"uid":218238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"必須解散警隊"},{"pid":"4394cd8431b0216ce688ed6b268a71c1fc548b9c","tid":1612974,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:55:11